  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting the government in creating inclusive, responsive and resilient education systems in Nepal</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The problems of illiteracy, non-enrollment and school dropout varies by gender, region and different social and language groups in Nepal. UNESCO will support the government towards ensuring inclusive and equitable quality education for all. Nepal, being a linguistically diverse country, UNESCO will support the government of Nepal&apos;s endeavor in addressing various language issues towards ensuring the rights of indigenous people and linguistic minorities to quality basic and primary education through their mother tongue. Moreover, UNESCO will also support the government towards disaster preparedness and to ensure safe learning environment for all in pre-, post- and during the time of emergencies.</narrative>
  </description>
